All Implemented Interfaces:
Connectable, ObjectInfoPanel.Printable, SearchTreeObject, Drawable, ShapeTree.Storable, UndoableObjects.Storable, Serializable, Comparable<Object>
public class Pin extends DrillItem implements Serializable
Class describing the functionality of an electrical Item on the board with a shape on 1 or several layers.
